---
title: Sarh — Property approval (2/3) · Deed PDF + SSI VC + IPFS + NFT mint
---
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant API as .NET 8 API
    participant DB as SQL Server
    participant FS as Storage<br/>(local FS)
    participant PDF as PAdES signer
    participant SSI as ACA-Py<br/>(Hyperledger Aries)
    participant IPFS as IPFS<br/>(metadata pin)
    participant BC as Blockchain<br/>(Ethereum / Hyperledger)
    participant SC as Smart Contract<br/>(ERC-721)

    Note over API,SSI: 4) Deed PDF + SSI VC issuance
    API->>PDF: generate deed PDF<br/>(citizen, polygon, decree)
    PDF-->>API: signed PAdES bytes + SHA256
    API->>FS: write deeds/<id>.pdf
    API->>DB: UPDATE properties SET deed_pdf_path, deed_signed_hash
    API->>SSI: issue VC (PropertyDeed) for citizen DID
    SSI-->>API: credential_id
    API->>DB: UPDATE properties SET vc_credential_id

    Note over API,SC: 5) NFT licence minting on blockchain
    API->>API: build token metadata<br/>(propertyCode, polygon GeoJSON,<br/>deed SHA256, ownerDID, decree)
    API->>IPFS: pin metadata.json
    IPFS-->>API: ipfs://Qm…CID
    API->>BC: mint(toAddress, tokenId, tokenURI)
    BC->>SC: invoke mint()
    SC-->>BC: Transfer(0x0, owner, tokenId)
    BC-->>API: txHash + blockNumber
    API->>DB: INSERT property_nfts<br/>(token_id, contract, network, metadata_uri,<br/>mint_tx_hash, minted_by_manager_id)
    API->>DB: INSERT ownership_history<br/>(from=null, to=owner_did, reason='initial_mint')
    API->>DB: UPDATE properties SET status='minted'
    API->>DB: INSERT notifications (citizen, "deed + NFT licence ready")